requirements.spec:
In gleam/aion_kit/src/aion_kit/template.gleam, define join_blocks and join_lines. WHEN join_blocks(blocks) is called, THE SYSTEM SHALL drop every empty-string block and join the remainder with a blank line (

) between sections. WHEN join_lines(lines) is called, THE SYSTEM SHALL drop every empty-string line and join the remainder with a single newline (
). THE SYSTEM SHALL NOT collapse, trim, or reformat non-empty content, and SHALL NOT emit a leading or trailing separator. The module SHALL NOT import aion/workflow, aion/activity, aion/query, aion/signal, or examples/stacked-dev/prompts.gleam, and SHALL perform no IO.
